cursor-plugin — by Armert Labs (https://github.com/Armert-Labs)

This plugin wraps the Cursor CLI (`cursor-agent`) for use inside Claude Code.
Its command surface and runtime contract are inspired by OpenAI's codex-plugin-cc
(https://github.com/openai/codex-plugin-cc, Apache-2.0). No OpenAI code is
redistributed here; the implementation is original and licensed under MIT.

"Cursor" and "cursor-agent" are products of Anysphere, Inc. "Claude" and
"Claude Code" are products of Anthropic. This is an unofficial, community
plugin and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Anysphere or Anthropic.
